    "Name": "Dengier",
    "Details": "The DG1-OB loadout strips out the melee weapons entirely and fills that tonnage with an Ultra AC/20, making it the most straightforwardly dangerous close-range configuration in the Dengier lineup. An ER Large Laser and twin ER Medium Lasers back up the autocannon at longer ranges. Four tons of ammunition and CASE II give it solid sustained firepower without the explosion risk.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Protected Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.05</color></b>",
